---
import InternalPage from "../layouts/InternalPage.astro";
---

<InternalPage
	title="Giving Back"
	description="Discover how Commonwealth Audiology gives back by helping bring better hearing, connection, and hope to those who need it most."
	breadcrumbs={[
		{ label: "Home", href: "/" },
		{ label: "Giving Back" },
	]}
>
	<p class="lead-italic">
		At Commonwealth Audiology, we believe hearing is about so much more than
		sound. It's about connection.
	</p>
	<p>
		It's about hearing a loved one's voice, joining in on laughter, feeling
		confident in conversation, and staying connected to the world around you.
	</p>
	<p>
		For many people, those moments slowly fade when hearing loss goes
		untreated. And for some, access to hearing care simply isn't within reach.
	</p>
	<p>
		That is why Dr. Tiffany Brewer is proud to support <strong>Hearing the Call</strong>, a
		nonprofit organization dedicated to helping individuals receive the hearing
		care they need when they otherwise may not have the opportunity.
	</p>

	<h2>Why This Work Matters</h2>

	<div class="giveback-media-row">
		<div class="giveback-image-grid">
			<img src="/uploads/CWA-sensorineural.webp" alt="Audiologist fitting a patient with a hearing aid" />
			<img src="/uploads/CWA-Ear-wax-removal-683x1024.webp" alt="Ear wax removal procedure" />
			<img src="/uploads/CWA-tinnitus.webp" alt="Tinnitus evaluation and treatment" />
			<img src="/uploads/CWA-hearing-aid-fitting.webp" alt="Hearing aid fitting consultation" />
		</div>
		<div class="giveback-why">
			<p class="giveback-label">GIFT OF HEARING</p>
			<p>The gift of hearing can change a life in ways that are hard to measure. It can mean:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>A grandparent hearing a grandchild say, "I love you."</li>
				<li>Returning to church, family dinners, or conversations with friends.</li>
				<li>Feeling included again.</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				Hearing loss can be isolating. It can create distance in relationships,
				uncertainty in daily life, and a quiet sense of disconnect from the people
				and moments that matter most.
			</p>
			<p>
				Through Hearing the Call, individuals are given more than hearing care. They
				are given the chance to reconnect, participate, and feel like themselves
				again.
			</p>
			<a href="https://www.hearingthecall.org/colorado/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="giveback-donate-btn">DONATE TO HEARING THE CALL</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="giveback-video-wrap">
		<iframe
			src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3enhHe4UXJU?controls=1&rel=0"
			title="What is Hearing the Call?"
			allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
			allowfullscreen
		></iframe>
	</div>

	<div class="giveback-cards-row">
		<div class="giveback-card">
			<h2>A Mission Close to the Heart</h2>
			<p>
				For Dr. Brewer, supporting Hearing the Call reflects the heart behind
				Commonwealth Audiology's work each day. Providing expert care is important,
				but so is compassion, service, and making sure people feel seen, heard, and
				cared for.
			</p>
			<p>Giving back is a meaningful extension of that mission.</p>
			<p>
				It is a reminder that hearing care has the power to do more than improve
				communication. It can restore confidence, strengthen families, and open the
				door to life's everyday joys once again.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="giveback-card">
			<h2>Changing Lives, One Person at a Time</h2>
			<p>
				At Commonwealth Audiology, we have the privilege of seeing firsthand how
				better hearing can transform lives. It's in the smile of recognition, the
				relief of finally understanding conversation again, and the joy of
				reconnecting with familiar voices.
			</p>
			<p>
				That is why we are honored to support an organization like Hearing the Call,
				because everyone deserves the opportunity to experience those moments.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="giveback-cta-block">
		<div class="giveback-htc-logo">
			<img src="/uploads/Hearing-the-Call-Colorado-White.webp" alt="Hearing the Call Colorado" />
		</div>
		<h2>Giving Back Through Hearing the Call</h2>
		<p>
			If you feel inspired to learn more or would like to be part of this effort,
			we welcome you to reach out. Whether you have questions, want to get
			involved, or simply want to better understand how you can make a
			difference, our team is here to connect with you.
		</p>
		<p>
			<a href="/contact/">Contact Commonwealth Audiology</a> today to learn how you
			can help bring the gift of hearing to someone in need.
		</p>
		<p>
			To learn more about Hearing the Call and the impact they are making, visit
			<a href="https://www.hearingthecall.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hearingthecall.org</a>.
		</p>
	</div>
</InternalPage>

<style>
	.giveback-media-row {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 2rem;
		align-items: start;
		margin: 2rem 0;
	}

	.giveback-image-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.giveback-image-grid img {
		width: 100%;
		aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
		object-fit: cover;
		border-radius: 6px;
	}

	.giveback-label {
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: #0076ba;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.giveback-donate-btn {
		display: inline-block;
		margin-top: 1.25rem;
		padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
		background: #0076ba;
		color: #fff;
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.06em;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 4px;
		transition: background 0.2s;
	}

	.giveback-donate-btn:hover {
		background: #005a8e;
	}

	.giveback-video-wrap {
		position: relative;
		width: 100%;
		aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
		margin: 2.5rem 0;
		border-radius: 8px;
		overflow: hidden;
		background: #000;
	}

	.giveback-video-wrap iframe {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		border: 0;
	}

	.giveback-cards-row {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin: 2rem 0;
	}

	.giveback-card {
		background: #f7f9fc;
		border-radius: 10px;
		padding: 1.75rem;
	}

	.giveback-card h2 {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.giveback-cta-block {
		background: #1b3328;
		color: #fff;
		border-radius: 10px;
		padding: 2.5rem;
		margin: 2rem 0;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.giveback-cta-block h2 {
		color: #fff;
		font-size: 1.6rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.giveback-cta-block p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88); }

	.giveback-cta-block a {
		color: #7ec8f0;
	}

	.giveback-htc-logo {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.giveback-htc-logo img {
		height: 60px;
		width: auto;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.giveback-media-row,
		.giveback-cards-row {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
